Package com.game.core.utils

Class GameSceneLoader

java.lang.Object
com.game.core.utils.GameSceneLoader
public class GameSceneLoader extends Object
Responsible for loading and initializing game scenes from a configuration. This includes the setup of tiles, blocks, spawners, and areas in the game model.
